				<div class="serviceDetails">
					<h3> Intersection Counts </h3>
					Intersection Count reports on the directional volume of traffic as it moves through a signalized or unsignalized intersection.Also called a Turning Movement Count (TMC), our Intersection Count study tabulates the number of left-turn, right-turn, u-turn and through movements for each leg.
				</div>
