				<img class="serviceImage" src="images/services/roundabout-counts.jpg" alt="Roundabout Counts">
				<div class="serviceDetails">
					<h3> Roundabout Counts </h3>
					Roundabout Count Report totals the turning movement volume (TMV) of a roundabout, detailing the entry, circulating and exit flow rate for each roundabout leg, from origin to destination. This data can be used to determine the capacity and performance efficiency of the different roundabout approaches, and the roundabout as a whole.</div>
			</td>
		</tr>
